These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: almond-milk, juice
Movie-Genre: adventure, epic
Sport: cricket, rugby
Transport: ship, van
1. Transport:van is on the left or right of Sport:rugby##3
2. Beverage:juice is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:epic == Beverage:almond-milk##1
4. Transport:van is on the right of Transport:ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | juice   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | adventure   |
| Sport         | rugby | cricket |
| Transport     | ship | van    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: kiwi, pepper
Movie-Genre: epic, mystery
Pet: rabbit, goldfish
Transport: skateboard, car
1. Pet:goldfish is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:epic == Transport:car##1
3. Food:pepper is on the right of Movie-Genre:mystery##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | kiwi     | pepper |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | epic  |
| Pet           | goldfish         | rabbit     |
| Transport     | skateboard   | car    |

 #################################
 
