3. Job:journalist == Nationality:chinese##1
4. Pet:goat is on the left of Nationality:german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | journalist | accountant    |
| Nationality   | chinese       | german |
| Pet           | goat         | goldfish    |
| Sport         | swimming    | biathlon   |

